# Content QA Agent — environment config.
#
# Copy this to a real .env in this folder and fill in YOUR key. Never commit
# the real .env — it's already in .gitignore. Your key never leaves your
# machine: every call goes straight from this script to the provider you
# choose below, nothing routes through anyone else's server.
#
#     cp .env.example .env
#     $EDITOR .env
#
# You do NOT need this file to run the offline checks (grammar heuristics +
# voice/fact heuristics) — those work with zero configuration. This unlocks
# the deeper LLM-powered layers: richer grammar/style catches, voice-drift
# rewrites, LLM-judged fact verdicts, and the voice-profile wizard.

# --- Pick ONE provider -------------------------------------------------------
# Anthropic (Claude) — get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# OR OpenRouter (any model, incl. Claude/GPT/Gemini) — https://openrouter.ai/keys
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=

# --- Optional overrides -------------------------------------------------------
# Force a provider if you've set both keys above (default: anthropic wins).
# LLM_PROVIDER=anthropic

# Override the default model for your chosen provider.
# LLM_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5
